Class DynamicThemeWork

java.lang.Object
androidx.work.ListenableWorker
androidx.work.Worker
com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.support.theme.work.DynamicThemeWork
public class DynamicThemeWork extends Worker
Worker class to change dynamic theme according to the time.

It will be useful in updating the auto theme while the app is in background.
